comments: Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Huerter's (ATL) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Butler (MIA) makes slight contact with Young (ATL) during the rebound,
Butler (MIA) makes slight contact with Len (ATL) as he cuts through the lane.
Butler (MIA) has a resting hand on Young's (ATL) body during his drive.
Adebayo (MIA) is firming up and makes slight contact with Hunter's (ATL) during the dribble handoff.
Hunter (ATL) makes contact to Butler's (MIA) head during his driving shot attempt.
Len (ATL) and Adebayo (MIA) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Len (ATL) establishes himself in Jones Jr.'s (MIA) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Nunn (MIA) sets a wide screen on Hunter (ATL) prior to the inbound pass.
Huerter (ATL) makes marginal contact to Butler (MIA) at the end of his drive.
Robinson (MIA) slides his pivot foot prior to his shot attempt.
Jones Jr. (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Bembry's (ATL) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Parker (ATL) establishes himself in Jones Jr.'s (MIA) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Bembry (ATL) makes marginal contact with Butler (MIA) as Butler secures the inbounds pass.
Nunn (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hunter (ATL) and does not deliver contact.
ATL commits a 24 second violation. After Replay Review the game clock is reset to 00:05.8.
Butler (MIA) releases from Bembry (ATL) at the end of his drive that does not dislodge Bembry from his position.
